地位，更便宜的型號將幫助它瞄准更廣泛的受眾。<br />\n<br />\n另外，2020 年的新款 iPad Air 可能是第一個拋棄 Lightning 端口的非 Pro 機型。當前型號的 iPad Air 配備 10.5 英吋屏，內部搭載 A12 仿生。儘管不知道後繼產品是否會在物理尺寸上變大，還是會縮窄其邊框以增加屏幕尺寸，但後者的可能性似乎更大。<br />\nimage<br />\n台灣的瑞儀光電將為即將到來的平板提供背光單元（BLU），屏幕訂單將在 LG Display，京東方和夏普之間進行分配。<br />\n<br />\n根據以前的傳言，新的 iPad Air 可能會採用 Face ID 或屏下指紋，並且可能還會過渡到 USB-C 端口，也有人猜測新型號將與妙控鍵盤相兼容。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T01:13:06.000Z","msg":"哇,iPad air愈變愈大mon ,會唔會考慮下用mac os system&bull;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T02:11:56.000Z","msg":"有都應該得ipad pro 有，air 用到2代keyboard，筆 同轉usbc 已經偷笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T15:02:27.000Z","msg":"咪ff 34千蚊唔會俾新design你用"},{"pid":"b6b0dbde06778fdfc86f7bd75399728180a68cf3","tid":2112954,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b107c23fd816664c7df1d619ee71632b3b654e48","tid":2112954,"uid":68728,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"14c902c08695674abf9ab43a54a3eb83ba00d122","tid":2112954,"uid":9387,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"44b8e663722eb11b9d80e2df4e23829fea8afff9","tid":2112954,"uid":229459,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T02:24:04.000Z","msg":"改用type-c已經係最大升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLightning 嘅話想做多啲嘢都唔得<br />\n過文件、駁mon、插mouse keyboard用lightning 嘅話係煩到爆"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T02:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WQqaMi3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWQqaMi3.jpg&h=7d175063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:19:18.000Z","msg":"啲idog係唔係弱智？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac